@node Introduct
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
ViewPCX is an image  viewer  for  PICASSO  II  gfxboards.  It  handles
PCX-files  with  1  to  4  Bitplanes  (2-16  Colors)  and  1,  3 and 4
Colorplanes (= 8/24/32 Bitdepth).
@endnode

